(45,	1,	'2026-03-09 12:17:37',	'2026-03-09 12:17:37',	'Indulge in our signature Organic Chocolate Cake — a masterpiece of rich, velvety layers crafted from 70% dark cacao sourced from sustainable farms. Each slice is moist, dense, and finished with a silky ganache glaze. Free from artificial preservatives, this cake is as wholesome as it is indulgent. Perfect for celebrations or a quiet moment of self-care.',	'Organic Chocolate Cake Slice',	'A rich and decadent chocolate cake made with organic ingredients.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'organic-chocolate-cake-slice',	'',	'',	'2026-03-09 12:20:20',	'2026-03-09 12:20:20',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/organic-chocolate-cake-slice/',	39,	'product',	'',	0),
