(47,	1,	'2026-03-09 12:17:39',	'2026-03-09 12:17:39',	'Hand-picked at peak ripeness from certified organic farms, our strawberries burst with natural sweetness and vibrant flavor. No pesticides, no additives — just pure, sun-kissed fruit. Great for smoothies, desserts, salads, or simply enjoyed fresh. Delivered same-day to preserve maximum freshness.',	'Fresh Organic Strawberries',	'Juicy and sweet organic strawberries, perfect for snacking or desserts.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'fresh-organic-strawberries',	'',	'',	'2026-03-10 10:27:48',	'2026-03-10 10:27:48',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/fresh-organic-strawberries/',	30,	'product',	'',	0),
