(59,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:20:34',	'2026-03-15 14:20:34',	'Our Mixed Organic Nuts are slow-roasted at low temperatures to preserve their natural oils and crunch. Featuring a handpicked blend of cashews, almonds, walnuts, and hazelnuts — all certified organic and free from added salt or preservatives. Rich in protein, healthy fats, and minerals. A perfect everyday snack for the health-conscious.',	'Mixed Organic Nuts',	'A premium blend of organic cashews, almonds, walnuts, and hazelnuts.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'mixed-organic-nuts',	'',	'',	'2026-03-17 06:07:42',	'2026-03-17 06:07:42',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/mixed-organic-nuts/',	37,	'product',	'',	0),
(60,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:20:34',	'2026-03-15 14:20:34',	'Our Cold-Pressed Orange Juice is made from sun-ripened organic Valencia oranges, pressed without heat to retain every drop of Vitamin C, enzymes, and natural sweetness. No added sugar, no concentrates — just 100% pure juice. Bottled within hours of pressing and kept chilled for optimal freshness.',	'Cold-Pressed Orange Juice',	'Freshly squeezed organic oranges, cold-pressed to lock in vitamins.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'cold-pressed-orange-juice',	'',	'',	'2026-03-17 06:09:18',	'2026-03-17 06:09:18',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/cold-pressed-orange-juice/',	16,	'product',	'',	0),
(61,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:20:35',	'2026-03-15 14:20:35',	'Crafted using a 48-hour slow fermentation process, our Sourdough Loaf delivers a perfectly tangy flavor, open crumb structure, and a deeply caramelized crust. Made with just organic flour, water, and salt — no yeast, no additives. Rich in naturally occurring probiotics that support gut health. Slice it thick and pair with butter or avocado.',	'Sourdough Bread Loaf',	'Traditionally fermented sourdough with a crispy crust and chewy crumb.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'sourdough-bread-loaf',	'',	'',	'2026-03-17 06:12:12',	'2026-03-17 06:12:12',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/sourdough-bread-loaf/',	51,	'product',	'',	0),
