(63,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:20:36',	'2026-03-15 14:20:36',	'Our Green Detox Smoothie is cold-blended fresh daily using organic baby spinach, crisp cucumber, green apple, and a zingy knob of ginger. Naturally alkalizing and packed with chlorophyll, antioxidants, and digestive enzymes. No dairy, no protein powder — just clean, vibrant greens in every sip. Best enjoyed on an empty stomach for a full morning reset.',	'Green Detox Smoothie',	'A refreshing blend of spinach, cucumber, apple, and ginger.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'green-detox-smoothie',	'',	'',	'2026-03-17 08:05:08',	'2026-03-17 08:05:08',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/green-detox-smoothie/',	31,	'product',	'',	0),
