(94,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:24:58',	'2026-03-15 14:24:58',	'Our Organic Pomegranates are sourced from sun-drenched farms in Iran and Spain, where the arid climate produces fruit with the highest sugar-to-acid ratio. Each pomegranate is bursting with thousands of ruby arils packed with punicalagins — antioxidants three times more potent than red wine. Eat fresh, juice them, or scatter over salads and grain bowls.',	'Fresh Organic Pomegranate',	'Hand-selected organic pomegranates with ruby-red jewel-like arils.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'fresh-organic-pomegranate',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 16:47:26',	'2026-03-24 16:47:26',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/fresh-organic-pomegranate/',	28,	'product',	'',	0),
(95,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:00',	'2026-03-15 14:25:00',	'Our Rosemary Focaccia is slow-proofed for 24 hours to develop an open, airy crumb structure with a deeply golden, olive oil-crisped crust. Topped generously with fresh rosemary sprigs and flaky sea salt. Baked in cast iron for an even heat. Made with organic semolina flour and first-cold-press extra virgin olive oil. Tear and share, or serve alongside soups.',	'Rosemary Focaccia Bread',	'Pillowy Italian focaccia drizzled with olive oil and fresh rosemary.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'rosemary-focaccia-bread',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 16:48:35',	'2026-03-24 16:48:35',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/rosemary-focaccia-bread/',	50,	'product',	'',	0),
(96,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:01',	'2026-03-15 14:25:01',	'Our Ginger Lemon Kombucha is brewed for 21 days using a live SCOBY culture fed with organic green tea and raw cane sugar. The long fermentation produces a beautifully tart, effervescent base with naturally occurring probiotics, B vitamins, and organic acids. Finished with cold-pressed ginger and lemon. Lightly fizzy, gut-healing, and completely unpasteurized.',	'Kombucha — Ginger & Lemon',	'Raw fermented kombucha with organic ginger root and fresh lemon.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'kombucha-ginger-lemon',	'',	'',	'2026-04-20 15:46:53',	'2026-04-20 15:46:53',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/kombucha-ginger-lemon/',	33,	'product',	'',	0),
(97,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:02',	'2026-03-15 14:25:02',	'Sun-dried white mulberries from organic farms in Turkey and Uzbekistan — one of the most underappreciated superfoods. Naturally sweet with notes of honey and vanilla. Uniquely high in resveratrol, iron, and 1-deoxynojirimycin (DNJ) — a compound studied for blood sugar management. Eat by the handful, mix into yogurt, or add to baked goods.',	'Dried Mulberries White',	'Delicate sun-dried white mulberries with a honeyed, fig-like sweetness.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'dried-mulberries-white',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 16:56:42',	'2026-03-24 16:56:42',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/dried-mulberries-white/',	24,	'product',	'',	0),
(99,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:03',	'2026-03-15 14:25:03',	'A breathtaking magenta blend of frozen organic açaí from the Amazon and pink dragon fruit (pitaya) from Vietnam, blended smooth with young coconut milk. An antioxidant powerhouse with a gorgeous natural color and a mildly sweet, tropical flavor profile. Vegan, dairy-free, and loaded with betalains, anthocyanins, and healthy fats. Pure liquid vitality.',	'Açaí & Pitaya Smoothie',	'A vibrant blend of Amazonian açaí and dragon fruit with coconut milk.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'aa-pitaya-smoothie',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:02:08',	'2026-03-24 17:02:08',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/aa-pitaya-smoothie/',	1,	'product',	'',	0),
(100,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:04',	'2026-03-15 14:25:04',	'Our Lemon Poppy Seed Loaf is baked from a recipe that balances bright citrus punch with rich, buttery tenderness. Made with organic lemon zest and freshly squeezed juice, stone-ground flour, free-range eggs, and generous poppy seeds throughout. Finished with a translucent lemon-icing glaze. Serve in thick slices with afternoon tea or pack as a lunchbox treat.',	'Lemon Poppy Seed Loaf',	'Tender lemon loaf studded with poppy seeds and finished with lemon glaze.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'lemon-poppy-seed-loaf',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:03:15',	'2026-03-24 17:03:15',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/lemon-poppy-seed-loaf/',	34,	'product',	'',	0),
(101,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:07',	'2026-03-15 14:25:07',	'A bold, warming juice pressed from pounds of organic Nantes carrots, raw ginger root, and golden turmeric. Beta-carotene-rich and anti-inflammatory, this juice supports skin radiance, immune resilience, and digestive health. The ginger provides a long, spicy finish that lingers pleasantly. A staple in any serious wellness routine.',	'Cold-Pressed Carrot Ginger Juice',	'Vibrant cold-pressed juice with organic carrots, ginger, and turmeric.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'cold-pressed-carrot-ginger-juice',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:04:33',	'2026-03-24 17:04:33',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/cold-pressed-carrot-ginger-juice/',	13,	'product',	'',	0),
(102,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:08',	'2026-03-15 14:25:08',	'Our Organic Kiwis are grown in the fertile volcanic soils of New Zealand and Italy. Each fruit is harvested at full Brix maturity for the perfect sugar-acid balance — vibrant green flesh, edible skin packed with fiber, and a floral tartness unlike anything else. One kiwi delivers more Vitamin C than an orange. Eat whole, slice into smoothie bowls, or toss into fruit salads.',	'Organic Kiwi Fruit',	'Tangy and vitamin-rich organic green kiwis, perfectly ripened.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'organic-kiwi-fruit',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:05:23',	'2026-03-24 17:05:23',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/organic-kiwi-fruit/',	41,	'product',	'',	0),
(103,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:08',	'2026-03-15 14:25:08',	'Our Yogurt Berry Parfait is assembled fresh each morning using thick, strained Greek yogurt from grass-fed cows, layered with wild blueberries and strawberries, and topped with our house-made honey oat granola. A drizzle of raw wildflower honey finishes each jar. High in protein, probiotics, and natural energy — the ideal breakfast-on-the-go in a glass jar.',	'Yogurt & Berry Parfait',	'Layered Greek yogurt parfait with wild berries, granola, and honey.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'yogurt-berry-parfait',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:06:12',	'2026-03-24 17:06:12',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/yogurt-berry-parfait/',	55,	'product',	'',	0),
(104,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:10',	'2026-03-15 14:25:10',	'Harvested from certified organic wolfberry bushes in the Ningxia region of China — the historical heartland of goji cultivation. Our Dried Goji Berries are sun-dried at low altitude to preserve zeaxanthin, polysaccharides, and all 18 amino acids. Slightly tart and chewy with a faint floral sweetness. Add to trail mix, porridge, or brew as a tea.',	'Dried Goji Berries',	'Vibrant red dried goji berries — a legendary superfood from the Himalayas.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'dried-goji-berries',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:07:58',	'2026-03-24 17:07:58',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/dried-goji-berries/',	22,	'product',	'',	0),
(105,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:12',	'2026-03-15 14:25:12',	'Our Turmeric Golden Latte is an ancient Ayurvedic recipe brought to life in a bottle. Organic turmeric powder and whole-root extract, Ceylon cinnamon, a precise pinch of black pepper to enhance curcumin bioavailability, and cold-pressed oat milk. Anti-inflammatory, warming, and subtly spiced. Enjoy hot or cold — a ritual for morning and evening alike.',	'Turmeric Golden Latte',	'Warming golden milk with turmeric, cinnamon, black pepper, and oat milk.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'turmeric-golden-latte',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:09:18',	'2026-03-24 17:09:18',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/turmeric-golden-latte/',	53,	'product',	'',	0),
(106,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:12',	'2026-03-15 14:25:12',	'Our Spelt Walnut Loaf uses ancient-grain whole spelt flour — lower in gluten, higher in protein and minerals than modern wheat. Naturally leavened with our sourdough starter and generously loaded with toasted California walnuts and golden flaxseeds. Dense, complex, and immensely satisfying. Slice thin and top with ricotta and honey, or enjoy with aged cheddar.',	'Spelt & Walnut Loaf',	'Dense, nutty spelt loaf studded with toasted walnuts and flaxseeds.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'spelt-walnut-loaf',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:10:24',	'2026-03-24 17:10:24',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/spelt-walnut-loaf/',	52,	'product',	'',	0),
(107,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:13',	'2026-03-15 14:25:13',	'Our Black Mission Figs are tree-ripened on certified organic farms in California and Turkey, harvested only when the skin begins to crack and the natural sugars concentrate at their peak. Each fig is soft, jammy, and overflowing with floral sweetness. Rich in calcium, magnesium, and prebiotic fiber. Eat fresh, pair with prosciutto and cheese, or halve and roast with honey.',	'Fresh Organic Figs',	'Lush, honey-sweet organic black mission figs, in season and tree-ripened.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'fresh-organic-figs',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:11:50',	'2026-03-24 17:11:50',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/fresh-organic-figs/',	26,	'product',	'',	0),
(108,	1,	'2026-03-15 14:25:14',	'2026-03-15 14:25:14',	'From the sun-scorched pistachio orchards of Kerman, Iran — where the finest pistachios in the world have been cultivated for over 3,000 years. Our Roasted Salted Pistachios are dry-roasted at precise temperatures to achieve the ideal crack-and-peel shell experience, then lightly seasoned with sea salt. Rich in lutein, protein, and fiber. Snack mindfully.',	'Pistachio Nuts Roasted & Salted',	'Crunchy roasted pistachios in shell, lightly salted with sea salt.',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'pistachio-nuts-roasted-salted',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:12:55',	'2026-03-24 17:12:55',	'',	0,	'https://server-coomendem.local/product/pistachio-nuts-roasted-salted/',	48,	'product',	'',	0),
