(160,	1,	'2026-03-24 16:44:48',	'2026-03-24 16:44:48',	'Our Blueberry Oat Muffins are baked fresh each morning with whole-grain oat flour, organic wild blueberries, and a bright finish of fresh lemon zest. Refined sugar-free — sweetened only with ripe banana and raw honey. Moist, tender, and packed with fiber. A guilt-free bake that genuinely satisfies. Perfect for lunchboxes or mid-morning snacking.',	'Blueberry & Oat Muffins',	'Moist oat muffins bursting with organic blueberries and lemon zest.',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'93-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 16:44:48',	'2026-03-24 16:44:48',	'',	93,	'https://server-coomendem.local/?p=160',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
