(163,	1,	'2026-03-24 16:50:55',	'2026-03-24 16:50:55',	'Our Ginger Lemon Kombucha is brewed for 21 days using a live SCOBY culture fed with organic green tea and raw cane sugar. The long fermentation produces a beautifully tart, effervescent base with naturally occurring probiotics, B vitamins, and organic acids. Finished with cold-pressed ginger and lemon. Lightly fizzy, gut-healing, and completely unpasteurized.',	'Kombucha — Ginger & Lemon',	'Raw fermented kombucha with organic ginger root and fresh lemon.',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'96-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 16:50:55',	'2026-03-24 16:50:55',	'',	96,	'https://server-coomendem.local/?p=163',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
