(178,	1,	'2026-03-24 17:14:20',	'2026-03-24 17:14:20',	'Pressed from organic celery stalks, English cucumbers, and a squeeze of fresh lime, this is the quintessential alkalizing green juice. Celery is rich in phthalides for blood pressure support; cucumber provides silica for skin and joint health. Zero sugar, zero additives — just pure, hydrating green goodness. Best consumed first thing in the morning on an empty stomach.',	'Cold-Pressed Celery & Cucumber Juice',	'Clean and alkalizing cold-pressed juice with celery, cucumber, and lime.',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'109-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2026-03-24 17:14:20',	'2026-03-24 17:14:20',	'',	109,	'https://server-coomendem.local/?p=178',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
